skills.name: Thorned Snare
skills.description: Deals Lightning DMG equal to ****1[i]%**** of ATK to one enemy and Lightning DMG equal to ****2[i]%**** of ATK to adjacent targets.

skills.name: A Body Brewed by Tears
skills.description: After attacking an enemy afflicted with "Seam Stitch," increases this unit's SPD by ****1[i]****, stacking up to **3[i]** time(s). When Garmentmaker takes action, automatically uses "Thorned Snare," prioritizing enemies under the "Seam Stitch" state.

skills.name: The Speeding Summer
skills.description: When Garmentmaker is summoned, this unit's **action advances** by **1[i]%**.

skills.name: Bloom of Drying Grass
skills.description: When Garmentmaker disappears, regenerates **1[i]** Energy for Aglaea.

skills.name: Claw Splits the Veil
skills.description: Deals Quantum DMG equal to ****1[f1]%**** of Castorice's Max HP to all enemies.

skills.name: Breath Scorches the Shadow
skills.description:
Launching "Breath Scorches the Shadow" will consume **1[i]%** of Netherwing's Max HP to deal Quantum DMG equal to ****2[f1]%**** of Castorice's Max HP to all enemies.
In one attack, "Breath Scorches the Shadow" can be launched repeatedly, with the DMG multiplier increased progressively to ****3[f1]%**** / ****4[f1]%****. After reaching ****4[f1]%****, it will not increase further. The DMG Multiplier Boost effect will not decrease before Netherwing disappears.
When Netherwing's current HP is equal to or less than **5[i]%** of its Max HP, launching this ability will actively reduce HP down to 1, and then trigger the ability effect equal to that of the Talent "Wings Sweep the Ruins."

skills.name: Mooncocoon Shrouds the Form
skills.description: When Netherwing is on the field, it acts as **backup** for allies. When allies take DMG or consume HP, their current HP can be reduced down to a minimum of 1, after which Netherwing will bear the HP loss. But Netherwing consumes HP equal to **1[i]%** of the original value. This lasts until Netherwing disappears.

skills.name: Roar Rumbles the Realm
skills.description: When Netherwing is summoned, increases DMG dealt by all allies by **1[i]%**, lasting for **2[i]** turn(s).

skills.name: Wings Sweep the Ruins
skills.description: When Netherwing disappears, deals **2[i]** instance(s) of DMG, with each instance dealing Quantum DMG equal to ****1[f1]%**** of Castorice's Max HP to one random enemy. At the same time, restores HP by an amount equal to ****3[i]%**** of Castorice's Max HP plus ****4[i]**** for all allies.

skills.name: Wings Sweep the Ruins
skills.description: Consumes all HP and deals **2[i]** instance(s) of DMG, with each instance dealing Quantum DMG equal to ****1[f1]%**** of Castorice's Max HP to one random enemy. At the same time, restores HP by an amount equal to ****3[i]%**** of Castorice's Max HP plus ****4[i]**** for all allies.

skills.name: Rainclouds, Time to Go!
skills.description: Deals Wind DMG to all enemies by an amount equal to ****1[i]%**** of the tally of healing done by Hyacine and Little Ica in the current battle, and clears **2[i]%** of this tally of healing.

skills.name: Take Sky in Hand
skills.description:
Little Ica maintains 0 SPD, is immune to **debuffs**, and will not appear in the Action Order.
If the HP of an ally target (except Little Ica) is reduced, then at the start of any target's turn or after any target takes action, Little Ica will consume **1[i]%** of their own Max HP and heal the ally target with reduced HP for an amount equal to ****2[f1]%**** of Hyacine's Max HP plus ****3[i]****.
While Hyacine is in the "After Rain" state, Little Ica gains 1 **extra turn** and automatically casts "Rainclouds, Time to Go!" immediately after Hyacine uses an ability. Moreover, when Little Ica triggers the Talent's healing effect, additionally restores HP for all ally targets by an amount equal to ****4[f1]%**** of Hyacine's Max HP plus ****5[i]****. After Little Ica uses an ability, the duration of all their **Continuous Effects** decreases by 1 turn.

skills.name: Soar, Unto the Sunlight
skills.description: When summoned, regenerates **1[i]** Energy for Hyacine. On the first summon, additionally regenerates **2[i]** Energy.

skills.name: Fall, Then Take Wing
skills.description: Upon disappearing, **advances the action** of Hyacine by **1[i]%**.

skills.name: Remembrance, Whirling, Like Rain
skills.description: This ability automatically selects a target, prioritizing the enemy target that Evernight last attacked. Deals Ice DMG equal to ****1[i]%**** of Evey's Max HP to one enemy. For every **3[i]** "Memoria" Evernight currently has, further deals Ice DMG equal to ****2[f1]%**** of Evey's Max HP. After use, Evernight gains **4[i]** "Memoria."

skills.name: Solitude, Drifting, In Murk
skills.description: Evey is immune to **Crowd Control debuffs** and has an increased chance of getting attacked. While Evey is on the field, Evernight and Evey deal ****1[i]%**** increased DMG.

skills.name: Night, Trailing, In Step
skills.description: When summoned, this unit immediately takes action.

skills.name: You, Parting, Beyond Reach
skills.description: Upon disappearing, increases Evernight's SPD by **1[i]%**. If the disappearance is due to using "Dream, Dissolving, as Dew," then, for every 1 "Memoria" point consumed by the attack, additionally increases Evernight's SPD by **2[i]%**. Up to **3[i]** "Memoria" points can be taken into account for this. The SPD Boost effect cannot stack and is removed at the start of Evernight's next turn.

skills.name: Dream, Dissolving, as Dew
skills.description: This ability is used when Evernight's "Memoria" is greater than or equal to **3[i]** and she is not affected by Crowd Control. For every 1 "Memoria" point currently held, deals Ice DMG equal to ****1[f1]%**** of Evey's Max HP to the primary target, and Ice DMG equal to ****2[f1]%**** of Evey's Max HP to the other enemy targets. After use, consumes all "Memoria" and HP, and makes Evey disappear.

skills.name: Baddies! Trouble!
skills.description: Deals **2[i]** instance(s) of DMG, with each instance dealing Ice DMG equal to ****1[f1]%**** of Mem's ATK to one random enemy. At the end, deals Ice DMG equal to ****3[i]%**** of Mem's ATK to all enemies.

skills.name: Friends! Together!
skills.description:
Increases all allies' CRIT DMG by an amount equal to ****1[f1]%**** of Mem's CRIT DMG plus ****2[f1]%****.
If the Charge has yet to reach **100%**, Mem automatically uses "Baddies! Trouble!" when taking action. When the Charge reaches **100%**, Mem immediately takes action. In the next action, can select one ally and use "Lemme! Help You!".

skills.name: Go, Mem, Go!
skills.description: When Mem is summoned, immediately gains **1[i]%** Charge.

skills.name: No... Regrets
skills.description: When Mem disappears, Trailblazer's **action advances** by **1[i]%**.

skills.name: Lemme! Help You!
skills.description:
**Advances the action** of one designated ally by **3[i]%** and grants them "Mem's Support," lasting for **2[i]** turn(s).
For every 1 instance of DMG dealt by a target that has "Mem's Support," additionally deals 1 instance of **True DMG** equal to ****1[i]%**** of the original DMG.
When using this ability on this unit, cannot trigger the **action advance** effect.
